In[18]:
def tags_to_consider(n):
    tag_i_sum = tag_bow.sum(axis=0).tolist()[0]
    sorted_tags_i = sorted(range(len(tag_i_sum)), key=lambda i: tag_i_sum[i], reverse=True)
    yn_multilabel=tag_bow[:,sorted_tags_i[:n]]
    return yn_multilabel

def content_covered_fn(numb):
    yn_multilabel = tags_to_consider(numb)
    x= yn_multilabel.sum(axis=1)
    return (np.count_nonzero(x==0))

In[53]:
def extract_named_entities(text):
    clean_text = re.sub(r'[^a-zA-Z\s]+', ' ', text)
    ner_result = ner(clean_text)
    entities = []
    for word, pos_tag, chunk_tag, ner_tag in ner_result:
        if ner_tag in ['B-PER']:
            entities.append(word)
    return ','.join(entities)

def test_named_entity_recognition():
    """
    Hm kim tra Underthesea NER c hot ng thnh cng khng.
    """
    # Vn bn mu  test
    test_text = "Nguyn Vn A ang lm vic ti cng ty VinGroup  H Ni."
    
    try:
        # Gi hm NER ca Underthesea
        ner_result = ner(test_text)
        
        # Hin th kt qu
        print("Kt qu phn tch NER:")
        for item in ner_result:
            # Mi item l mt tuple c th cha nhiu gi tr (t, nhn thc th, ...)
            if len(item) >= 2:
                word, entity = item[0], item[3]
                print(f"{word} -> {entity}")
            else:
                print(f"Khng r cu trc: {item}")
        
        # Xc nhn thnh cng
        print("\nUnderthesea NER hot ng thnh cng!")
    except Exception as e:
        # In li nu khng thnh cng
        print(f"Li xy ra: {e}")
        print("Underthesea NER khng hot ng!")

# Gi hm test
test_named_entity_recognition()

 -> O

def extract_ner_and_tokens():
    # Bc 1: Thc hin NER  nhn din thc th
    text = "Nguyn Vn A ang lm vic ti cng ty VinGroup  H Ni."
    ner_result = ner(text)
    
    # Bc 2: Tch t bng word_tokenize
    tokens = word_tokenize(text, format="text").split()
    # Bc 3: Ly thng tin NER
    named_entities = []
    for item in ner_result:
        word, pos_tag, chunk_tag, ner_tag = item
        if ner_tag != 'O':
            word_tokens = word_tokenize(word, format="text").split()
            word = " ".join(word_tokens)
            word = word.lower() # Ch ly cc t c nhn thc th
            named_entities.append((word, ner_tag))
    
    return tokens, named_entities
extract_ner_and_tokens()

In[42]:
def extract_ner_and_tokens():
    # Bc 1: Vn bn u vo
    text = "Nguyn Vn A ang lm vic ti cng ty VinGroup  H Ni."
    
    # Bc 2: Thc hin NER  nhn din thc th
    ner_result = ner(text)
    
    # Bc 3: Tch t bng word_tokenize
    tokens = word_tokenize(text, format="text").split()
    
    # Bc 4: Kt hp token v nhn NER
    named_entities = []
    current_entity = []  # Tm lu cc token thuc cng mt thc th
    current_label = None  # Nhn thc th hin ti
    
    for word, pos_tag, chunk_tag, ner_tag in ner_result:
        if ner_tag.startswith('B-'):  # Bt u thc th mi
            if current_entity:
                # Lu thc th trc 
                named_entities.append((' '.join(current_entity), current_label))
            current_entity = [word]  # Khi to thc th mi
            current_label = ner_tag
        elif ner_tag.startswith('I-') and current_label == ner_tag:  # Tip tc thc th
            current_entity.append(word)
        else:
            if current_entity:
                # Lu thc th trc 
                named_entities.append((' '.join(current_entity), current_label))
            current_entity = []  # t li
            current_label = None

    # Thm thc th cui cng (nu c)
    if current_entity:
        named_entities.append((' '.join(current_entity), current_label))
    
    return tokens, named_entities

# Gi hm
tokens, named_entities = extract_ner_and_tokens()

print("Tokens:", tokens)
print("Named Entities:", named_entities)
